Interface ObjectContextNotifier.ObjectContextListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectContextNotifier.DefaultObjectContextListener
    Enclosing class:
    ObjectContextNotifier

    public static interface ObjectContextNotifier.ObjectContextListener
    Defines the interface which ObjectContext listeners must implement to receive notifications of relevant events.

    • Method Detail

      • onObjectsChanged

        void onObjectsChanged(ObjectContext context,
                    ObjectsChangedNotification changedObjects)
        Called when any set of objects have changed since the last event loop. Changes includes objects that have have been inserted, removed, updated, or refreshed.
        Parameters:
        context - the context in which the changed objects belong to
        changedObjects - a notification object containing the objects that have been inserted, removed, updated, or refreshed

      • onPreSave

        void onPreSave(ObjectContext context)
        Called when the context is about to be saved.
        Parameters:
        context - the context instance that will be saved

      • onPostSave

        void onPostSave(ObjectContext context,
              ChangedObjectsSet changedObjects)
        Called when the context has just been saved.
        Parameters:
        context - the context instance that has been saved
        changedObjects - a reference to a collection of the objects that have been changed
